title.narrative: 5.2 COMMUNICATION: INCREASED AWARENESS & ENGAGEMENT IN PROMOTING CHILD RIGHTS

description.narrative: Key actors and civil society, including children, adolescents and their families, are more aware of the needs of Palestinian children and are more engaged in alliances for child rights, which contributes to Access To Inclusive Social Protection, Access To Inclusive Social Protection (Covid), Learning, Skills, Participation And Engagement, Social Protection. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Community Engagement, Social And Behaviour Change, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building, Systems Strengthening To Leave No One Behind. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: By 2022, more vulnerable children have access to social protection systems and are supported to participate in society and realize their rights
